    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This powerplant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a broad torque curve and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN limited-slip differential. This example has received essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service. The chassis remains taut with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and neutral handling characteristics this platform is known for. While showing minor signs of use, its mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
