    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, accented by well-preserved trim, with only the minor, honest character marks one would expect from careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of cleanliness; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic feature\u2014from the climate control to the premium audio system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, resulting in a smooth, responsive drive and a quiet, confident engine. It offers the perfect blend of reliability and style for a driver who wants a high-quality vehicle without the showroom price tag. It is fully inspected, recently detailed, and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 36500.0,
