    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a harmonious blend of refined aesthetics and reliable performance. The interior remains exceptionally well-preserved, reflecting a history of attentive ownership, while the drivetrain has been rigorously vetted to ensure continued excellence on the road. This is a sophisticated choice for those seeking a high-caliber driving experience and lasting value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
